OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly dry
OL,6,Fand bright end to the day. It will be
OL,7,Fmostly dry and cloudy through the
OL,8,Fnight but with the chance of the odd
OL,9,Fshower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA largely dry start but
OL,12,Frather cloudy. Showers will develop,
OL,13,Fespecially from late morning onwards,
OL,14,Fand some of these will be heavy and
OL,15,Fperhaps thundery at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,18,Fon Sunday with a chance of showers.
OL,19,FSunny spells and a few showers on
OL,20,FMonday and Tuesday. Remaining cooler
OL,21,Fthan recent days.
